Vendored for spec 011 (Warm-Modern Facelift) per FR-003.

NOTE: This directory ships the LICENSE marker. The actual subsetted WOFF2 file
(Latin-1 + numerals subset, variable weight 400-800) MUST be placed at
fraunces-variable.woff2 by an operator with network access. Until then, the
@font-face declaration in tokens.css will fail to fetch and the browser will
fall back to the next family in the stack (Inter then system serif). This is
documented as a deferred-asset condition in specs/011-warm-modern-facelift/implementation-notes.md.
